# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzys7.rpy:15
translate chinese suzys7_d78eee80:

    # ss "Food, movies, a concert, the beach - all of that sounds fun to me."
    ss "吃饭、看电影、听演唱会、去海滩——这些听起来都挺好玩的。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzys7.rpy:16
translate chinese suzys7_f40e77d8:

    # ss "Probably the beach would be my favorite though."
    ss "不过海滩大概是我最喜欢的。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzys7.rpy:18
translate chinese suzys7_e58f9a0d:

    # ss "Just a whole day of hanging out, half-naked."
    ss "就那样光着上半身，整整一天闲逛。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzys7.rpy:19
translate chinese suzys7_ec7049b7:

    # ss "Swimming, tanning, making out in the sand."
    ss "游泳、晒太阳、在沙滩上亲热。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzys7.rpy:21
translate chinese suzys7_2da59617:

    # ss "Then at night, starting a fire, roast some hot dogs or something..."
    ss "然后到了晚上，生个篝火，烤点热狗之类的……"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzys7.rpy:23
translate chinese suzys7_a1eafcca:

    # ss "Mess around under the stars."
    ss "在星空下调情。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzys7.rpy:24
translate chinese suzys7_fb86b185:

    # ss "That sounds like the perfect date to me."
